{"tid":2228213,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中秋不快樂 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-10-03T11:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T11:28:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"34cbf494088a63834a04f455a3a0779314ed113c","tid":2228213,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201003/KY7HTSSUBVFUDNN5G25ERRQBFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201003%2FKY7HTSSUBVFUDNN5G25ERRQBFE%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=0267b3c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201003%2FKY7HTSSUBVFUDNN5G25ERRQBFE%2F&h=f307197e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201003/KY7HTSSUBVFUDNN5G25ERRQBFE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中秋不快樂 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9Ed95al3k5nTmyDEAkkcjqc8d1k=/1200x922/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U6YEOEKWOJFKJG7DJAZXUWFCNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9Ed95al3k5nTmyDEAkkcjqc8d1k%3D%2F1200x922%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU6YEOEKWOJFKJG7DJAZXUWFCNU.jpg&h=9890b50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於香港，從去年4月反送中開始，香港進入最黑暗時期，無數抗爭者被消失、被濫捕濫告，身心受創，有的失去自由，有的失去健康，有的踏上逃亡路，有的在逃亡路上被捕而送中&hellip;&hellip;無數家庭從此以後永遠不可能人月兩圓。有何快樂可言？<br />\n<br />\n中秋日，警員全日在銅鑼灣戒備，傍晚在百德新街一帶圍捕外出消遣的民眾。有兩母女跟朋友一起，去誠品書店購書及吃中秋晚餐，手上尚拎着裝有書籍的購物袋，卻跟其他路人一起，被警方拉起封鎖線後截查，百幾個人，只是如常行街，沒有示威，沒有抗議，沒有喊口號，無端被查身份證、影大頭相片，被滋擾一輪後，一部分人被放行，一部分人被捕捉。上述三人行中，只有母親被放行，女兒及朋友均被警方帶走。中秋晚，母親不知女兒被帶去甚麼地方，心焦如焚，能快樂嗎？<br />\n<br />\n香港並無戒嚴，民眾外出觸犯了哪一條法律？警察濫捕至此，難怪有人說，此刻香港比日治時期更暗無天日。<br />\n<br />\n極權統治下，哪有節日？哪有快樂？"},{"pid":"43289b6930f9b55ec922c4f47f8067d51e0640ef","tid":2228213,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}